[06:19.24]	Will hold at Windsor; so inform the lords:
[06:22.09]	But come yourself with speed to us again;
[06:24.95]	For more is to be said and to be done
[06:27.62]	Than out of anger can be uttered.
[06:29.99]WESTMORELAND	I will, my liege.
